outputs.output_descr: Jamaica's Second National Communication will be prepared based on the UNFCCC Guidelines for the preparation of national communications from Parties not included in Annex I of the Convention adopted at the 10th Conference of the Parties and are contained in Decision 17/CP.8.

project_title: Preparation of the SNC to the UNFCCC for Jamaica
